Close your eyes.

454
00:36:58,739 --> 00:37:00,556
<i>My wish is simple.</i>

455
00:37:00,556 --> 00:37:04,400
<i>I hope she has a smooth and peaceful life.</i>

456
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:10,389
<i>From this moment on,
may we always walk this road together.</i>

457
